rows.label: tev058201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Bobora what he found during his travels.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0001
rows.name:
In Noctilum, Bobora found rare and precious
sibercaseras mushroom. Only one grows every
hundred years![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0002
rows.name:
And at cave in Primordia, Bobora obtained
seldom-seen item called "auroran bone."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0003
rows.name:
Oh, and Bobora also come across "spirit wand,"
legendary artifact made by ancient Nopon,
near base of mountain in Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0004
rows.name: Sadly, none of these able to cure Henahena...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0005
rows.name:
Bobora have friend and Milly and others to thank
for that. Without friends, Henahena might never
have gotten well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0010
rows.name:
Henahena bounced Bobora to kingdom come, but
Bobora determined to propose and came right back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0011
rows.name:
Henahena got so very big while away!
Now Henahena look robust enough to survive any
illness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0012
rows.name:
Never again must Bobora wander great unknown
in search of miracle medicines. It is end of era.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0013
rows.name:
From now on, Bobora stick right here,
make lots of littlepon, and start proper family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058201_MSG0014
rows.name:
Stars have given blessing to Bobora and Henahena,
and blessing must not be wasted.[ST:wait ]
